<section id="faq" class="faq">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="section-description">Everything you need to know about creating viral videos from Reddit content</p>
        
        <div class="faq-grid">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">
                    <span>What are Video Tokens?</span>
                    <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24">
                        <path fill="currentColor" d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Video Tokens are credits that allow you to create and export videos. Each video you create and export uses one token. Tokens are refreshed monthly based on your subscription plan.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">
                    <span>Can I use any Reddit content?</span>
                    <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24">
                        <path fill="currentColor" d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>You can use any public Reddit content that follows our content guidelines. We recommend using posts that are engaging, have good discussion, and are appropriate for your target audience.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">
                    <span>What video formats are supported?</span>
                    <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24">
                        <path fill="currentColor" d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>We support all major short-form video formats including MP4, MOV, and WebM. Videos are optimized for TikTok, Instagram Reels, and YouTube Shorts with the correct aspect ratios and quality settings.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">
                    <span>Can I customize the video templates?</span>
                    <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24">
                        <path fill="currentColor" d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes! All plans include access to our template library. You can customize text, colors, animations, background music, and more to match your brand and style.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">
                    <span>What kind of support do you offer?</span>
                    <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24">
                        <path fill="currentColor" d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Starter plan users have access to our help center and email support. Pro plan users get priority support with faster response times and access to our advanced analytics dashboard.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">
                    <span>Can I cancel my subscription anytime?</span>
                    <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24">
                        <path fill="currentColor" d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes, you can cancel your subscription at any time. Your access will continue until the end of your current billing period, and you'll keep all your created videos.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>